<V3InteriorLayout
  title="About"
  eyebrow="Who is Maya"
  description="Award-winning electronic music artist Maya Fourteen — biography, sound and recognition."
>
  <p>
    Award-winning electronic music artist Maya Fourteen moves fluidly across electronic genres,
    shaping sound through performance, production and curation. With a solid international
    audience and performances across respected stages worldwide, her presence carries depth and
    unmistakable taste.
  </p>
  <p>
    Originally from the Amazon Basin in Mato Grosso, Brazil, Maya's sets are known for being
    emotionally driven and story-telling, blending deep tech, organic house and progressive
    sounds into journeys that build sets that grow on you.
  </p>

  <p class="section-title">Recognition</p>
  <p>
    Winner of the Nicole Moudaber Future Talent Award and selected for the Pete Tong Future Talent
    Program, both at IMS Ibiza 2025.
  </p>
</V3InteriorLayout>
